attempts.sparql_query: PREFIX atm: <https://data.nasa.gov/ontologies/atmonto/ATM#> SELECT?userCategoryAAL100?userCategoryCHQ2945 WHERE { atm:AAL100-201407150030 atm:userCategory?userCategoryAAL100. atm:CHQ2945-201407150047 atm:userCategory?userCategoryCHQ2945. }
attempts.query_explanation: This SPARQL query retrieves the user categories of flights AAL100 and CHQ2945. The query uses the atm:userCategory property to get the user categories of the two flights and returns the results as?userCategoryAAL100 and?userCategoryCHQ2945. The query does not limit the results, so it will return all user categories associated with the two flights.
